WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:10.900
Ah.

2
00:00:17.400 --> 00:00:18.900
Good morning, Lady Wang.

3
00:00:19.533 --> 00:00:22.466
It’s not early, Your Highness.

4
00:00:22.466 --> 00:00:24.000
I’ve been waiting for you for a while.

5
00:00:29.566 --> 00:00:31.166
May Your Highness be blessed with peace and prosperity.

6
00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:38.966
I heard the Emperor punished Consort Yan last night because of you.

7
00:00:39.100 --> 00:00:40.766
You did very well.

8
00:00:41.133 --> 00:00:43.433
Get up, thank you, Empress Dowager.

9
00:00:46.066 --> 00:00:50.133
The harem is no longer dominated by Consort Yan’s faction.

10
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:51.166
Empress Dowager.

11
00:00:51.166 --> 00:00:53.300
Actually, I didn’t do anything last night.

12
00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:55.500
It was the Emperor’s own decision.

13
00:00:56.333 --> 00:00:57.566
What kind of person is the Emperor?

14
00:00:57.866 --> 00:00:59.266
Do you think I don’t know?

15
00:00:59.566 --> 00:01:01.266
You don’t need to feel embarrassed.

16
00:01:01.533 --> 00:01:04.466
Getting the Emperor’s favor is your skill.

17
00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:07.000
I won’t blame you.

18
00:01:07.066 --> 00:01:09.600
But I really didn’t do anything.

19
00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:11.100
What are they really trying to do?

20
00:01:11.566 --> 00:01:14.766
It shouldn’t just be about watching Consort Yan’s misfortune.

21
00:01:18.333 --> 00:01:22.566
Don’t be afraid of the Emperor using you as a scapegoat.

22
00:01:22.666 --> 00:01:26.766
Rest assured, as long as you can stand up to Consort Yan,

23
00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.400
I will fully support you.

24
00:01:29.733 --> 00:01:30.633
Of course.

25
00:01:31.166 --> 00:01:32.800
In the past life, the Empress Dowager did this.

26
00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.233
It was to help me become the Empress.

27
00:01:37.466 --> 00:01:39.233
What does the Empress Dowager want me to do?

28
00:01:39.466 --> 00:01:42.900
Hmph, talking to smart people is straightforward.

29
00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:44.400
Very simple.

30
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.766
I want you to help me remove Consort Yang.

31
00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:52.800
It’s simple, but the Empress Dowager might not know.

32
00:01:52.933 --> 00:01:55.200
In my past life, under the Emperor’s protection,

33
00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:59.100
you never harmed a single hair on Consort Yan.

34
00:01:59.366 --> 00:02:02.466
This might not be appropriate.

35
00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:06.000
After all, the Emperor still loves Consort Yan.

36
00:02:07.266 --> 00:02:10.400
So it depends on your ability.

37
00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:14.700
Consort Yan’s ambitions must be eradicated.

38
00:02:16.966 --> 00:02:19.400
So, will you do it or not?

39
00:02:20.066 --> 00:02:21.600
The attack has been decided.

40
00:02:22.166 --> 00:02:23.233
Yesterday’s incident.

41
00:02:23.466 --> 00:02:26.300
Consort Yan probably sees me as a thorn in her side.

42
00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:29.200
From now on, it’s either her death or mine.

43
00:02:29.766 --> 00:02:30.566
Do it.

44
00:02:32.266 --> 00:02:33.333
I will do it.

45
00:02:33.333 --> 00:02:34.166
But—

46
00:02:34.900 --> 00:02:36.600
But, um—

47
00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.100
I have a condition.
